{{Mission Description|type=trailblaze|location="Universal Matrix" Great Tomb of the Nameless Titan|Dan Heng, your most trusted Express Guard, and the most reliable companion on your Trailblaze journey.<br />He accepted Earth's divine authority, solely to stand alongside you and the Chrysos Heir friends, facing the new world and the impending final clash together. Just knowing he's back in Amphoreus gives you not just one, but a hundred times more peace of mind.<br /><br />When his consciousness delves into the memoria tide where no one else can reach, he is the bedrock, the waves, and the frosty gales...<br />He is the Earth and all that exists upon it.<br />He came for you, and now you will both go for March.<br /><br />The blazing sun has shown the way. Press onward.}}
